articles.author: Stephen Sorace
articles.title: Graham dismisses Liz Cheney’s Trump warning, says ‘world will be truly on fire’ if Biden re-elected - Fox News
articles.description: Sen. Lindsey Graham warned that a second Biden term would leave America unrecognizable, while a Trump presidency would help secure the U.S. border.
